---
import SectionHeading from "@/components/SectionHeading.astro";
---

<section id="experience" class="scroll-mt-24 pt-4">
    <SectionHeading index="01" title="Experiencia"/>

    <div class="grid gap-3">
        <div class="group grid gap-2 rounded-lg border border-transparent p-4 transition-colors hover:border-border hover:bg-card/60 sm:grid-cols-[160px_1fr]">
            <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground sm:pt-1">
                2026 - present
            </p>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-base font-semibold text-foreground">
                    Ingeniero DevSecOps
                    <span class="text-primary">· Ceiba Software S.A.S.</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
                    Contribuí al desarrollo de soluciones de automatización e Inteligencia Artificial para optimizar procesos internos, además de trabajar en la mejora de pipelines CI/CD y herramientas del ecosistema DevSecOps de la compañía.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                    <span class="rounded border border-border bg-secondary/40 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">DevSecOps</span>
                    <span class="rounded border border-border bg-secondary/40 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">AI Automation</span>
                    <span class="rounded border border-border bg-secondary/40 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">n8n</span>
                    <span class="rounded border border-border bg-secondary/40 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">CI/CD</span>
                    <span class="rounded border border-border bg-secondary/40 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-foreground/80">Azure DevOps</span>
                </div>
